data.description: Welcome to this charming colonial home nestled in the sought-after community of Laurel Branch. Situated on a tranquil cul-de-sac, this meticulously maintained property offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. As you approach, you're greeted by the inviting front porch, ideal for enjoying morning coffee or relaxing evenings. Step inside to discover a spacious 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom layout spread over 2168 square feet of living space. The main level boasts a bright and airy atmosphere, with an open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living spaces. The modern kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring sleek granite countertops, modern appliances, and ample cabinet space. It effortlessly flows into the separate dining area, making entertaining a breeze. Adjacent to the kitchen, you'll find the cozy family room, perfect for gathering with loved ones. Step outside onto the deck, where you can soak in the serene views of the fenced-in backyard and flat lot, offering plenty of space for outdoor activities. Upstairs, the spacious primary bedroom awaits, complete with a luxurious ensuite bathroom featuring a soaking tub, separate shower, and vanity. Three additional bedrooms and another full bathroom complete the upper level, providing plenty of room for everyone. Conveniently located near a variety of amenities, including restaurants, schools, shopping centers, and more, this home offers the ideal blend of suburban tranquility and urban convenience. Don't miss your chance to make this gem your own – schedule a showing today and experience the beauty and comfort of colonial living at its finest!
